  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2881690">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2881690/" class="title-link">扑朔迷离的晚清</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2881690"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jyo/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u6460592-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jyo/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">jyo</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-22"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-22 22:40:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2881690_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本书是”杨天石近代史文存“系列中的第一部，是杨先生近三十年来历史杂文的结集。该系列丛书并非通史性著作，而是就某些重要问题做的专门讨论。第一部的时间跨度是从鸦片战争到清朝覆灭。  其中个人觉得比较精彩的论述有：  1. 关于戊戌变法的论述。如慈禧对维新运动的态度，光...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2881690/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2881690_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2881690_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7220452">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7220452/" class="title-link">细看深思</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7220452"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/caoxiaohai/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47101229-21.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/caoxiaohai/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">曹小海</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-02"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-02 17:40:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7220452_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  杨天石先生中文专业出身，而后转入历史研究，在发掘使用资料方面有其过人之处。本书中引用评介的许多资料、材料、档案都是国内少见或者难得一见的，而后得出的结论亦与寻常观点大有不同。  我想这一方面是杨先生功力深厚，分析深入透彻。毕竟那些材料使用前就要求研究者具有相...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
